race.comment: RUSTY ROCKET (2) is a promising type who notched his 4th career success when too good (22.50) at this track last time. Will go close again if runs up to latest. BLUE BUICK (1) finished his campaign in the minors over 381m at Cannington, overcoming a collision in running in a Grade 6 to finish third (22.59). Leading player again. ASTON CREMA (4) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Divot (22.59) in a Grade 5/6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from three starts. Can feature again. AUSSIE TAN (8) drops in journey and should be in the mix.
